1
00:00:43,640 --> 00:00:44,160
Yiyi.

2
00:00:44,880 --> 00:00:46,540
Tiandao Palace is destroyed.

3
00:00:46,640 --> 00:00:48,970
Hasn't the seal on A'yuan been lifted yet?

4
00:00:49,280 --> 00:00:50,400
The seal on him

5
00:00:50,480 --> 00:00:52,280
is based on Taishu Yi's cultivation

6
00:00:52,280 --> 00:00:53,960
and the blood of the Likong clan.

7
00:00:53,960 --> 00:00:56,620
It has nothing to do with Tiandao Palace itself.

8
00:00:56,800 --> 00:00:59,200
The Netherworld was originally unsealed.

9
00:00:59,200 --> 00:01:01,880
As long as Lanqi Moyuan absorbs enough demonic energy

10
00:01:01,880 --> 00:01:03,120
and returns to his peak,

11
00:01:03,120 --> 00:01:04,980
he could always shatter the seal.

12
00:01:05,040 --> 00:01:06,120
But unfortunately,

13
00:01:06,120 --> 00:01:07,880
before he could shatter the seal,

14
00:01:07,880 --> 00:01:09,940
the Netherworld was already sealed.

15
00:01:10,200 --> 00:01:11,920
Demonic energy is scarce in the world.

16
00:01:11,920 --> 00:01:13,320
Without enough support,

17
00:01:13,520 --> 00:01:14,780
he can't lift the seal.

18
00:01:15,120 --> 00:01:17,780
Even after his own demonic energy is exhausted,

19
00:01:18,039 --> 00:01:18,960
what will dissipate

20
00:01:18,960 --> 00:01:19,840
is his life.

21
00:01:22,920 --> 00:01:24,320
Is there no way to lift it?

22
00:01:25,160 --> 00:01:27,420
Only the purest source blood can lift it.

23
00:01:27,800 --> 00:01:29,930
But the Likong clan is almost extinct.

24
00:01:30,000 --> 00:01:31,330
The only one who can do it

25
00:01:31,600 --> 00:01:32,530
is probably you.

26
00:01:34,880 --> 00:01:36,800
Then I must hurry back and help him lift it.

27
00:01:36,800 --> 00:01:39,120
The amount of blood needed to lift the seal is too massive.

28
00:01:39,120 --> 00:01:42,320
It can't be lifted in one, two, or even dozens of attempts.

29
00:01:44,320 --> 00:01:45,720
If you decide to help him,

30
00:01:47,160 --> 00:01:48,160
then you might

31
00:01:49,120 --> 00:01:50,580
have to stay in this world.

32
00:01:54,560 --> 00:01:55,360
Does he know?

33
00:01:56,759 --> 00:01:57,479
He knows.

34
00:02:18,160 --> 00:02:18,920
Why?

35
00:02:20,600 --> 00:02:22,000
Why won't you let me stay?

36
00:02:25,960 --> 00:02:27,490
You still have attachments

37
00:02:27,960 --> 00:02:28,760
in that world.

38
00:02:30,920 --> 00:02:31,560
Do you know

39
00:02:32,240 --> 00:02:33,500
what will happen to you

40
00:02:33,760 --> 00:02:35,079
if I leave?

41
00:02:39,880 --> 00:02:41,410
If you're not in this world,

42
00:02:42,120 --> 00:02:43,250
whether I live or die

43
00:02:43,720 --> 00:02:44,650
is meaningless.

44
00:02:48,560 --> 00:02:49,160
So,

45
00:02:51,240 --> 00:02:52,900
you still won't ask me to stay?

46
00:02:54,240 --> 00:02:54,880
I hope

47
00:02:55,720 --> 00:02:57,380
you can go where you want to go,

48
00:02:57,640 --> 00:02:58,840
do what you want to do,

49
00:02:59,880 --> 00:03:01,080
and leave no regrets.

50
00:03:03,680 --> 00:03:06,480
I know the pain of being separated from loved ones.

51
00:03:08,080 --> 00:03:10,410
I don't want you to experience what I have.

52
00:03:17,640 --> 00:03:18,800
Firmly live

53
00:03:19,440 --> 00:03:20,880
the life you want.

54
00:03:42,680 --> 00:03:43,610
It's about time.

55
00:03:44,240 --> 00:03:45,040
You should go.

56
00:03:52,600 --> 00:03:54,000
Don't you want to go back?

57
00:03:56,040 --> 00:03:56,760
No.

58
00:03:57,640 --> 00:03:59,500
Then what are you hesitating for?

59
00:04:01,200 --> 00:04:02,330
I don't know either.

60
00:04:04,560 --> 00:04:05,090
Lu Danyu,

61
00:04:06,040 --> 00:04:07,240
it's nice to meet you.

62
00:04:09,800 --> 00:04:10,640
I just feel

63
00:04:11,200 --> 00:04:13,000
I should also say goodbye to you.

64
00:04:16,720 --> 00:04:17,399
Yiyi.

65
00:04:18,360 --> 00:04:18,920
Lu Danyu,

66
00:04:19,360 --> 00:04:21,620
you really are a very interesting human.

67
00:04:21,839 --> 00:04:23,300
You changed Lanqi Moyuan,

68
00:04:23,680 --> 00:04:24,960
changed the trajectory,

69
00:04:24,960 --> 00:04:26,420
and saved the whole world.

70
00:04:26,880 --> 00:04:27,720
Without you,

71
00:04:27,840 --> 00:04:29,570
this world would turn to ashes.

72
00:04:30,360 --> 00:04:32,520
On behalf of the creatures of this world,

73
00:04:32,520 --> 00:04:33,600
I thank you.

74
00:04:35,240 --> 00:04:35,760
No.

75
00:04:36,040 --> 00:04:37,100
I'm not that great.

76
00:04:37,680 --> 00:04:38,560
I'm just

77
00:04:38,920 --> 00:04:40,580
doing what I think I should do.

78
00:04:42,120 --> 00:04:42,480
And

79
00:04:43,200 --> 00:04:43,730
Lu Danyu,

80
00:04:44,400 --> 00:04:45,000
I'm sorry.

81
00:04:46,560 --> 00:04:47,159
Yiyi,

82
00:04:48,000 --> 00:04:50,200
why are you suddenly apologizing to me?

83
00:04:50,440 --> 00:04:51,880
According to our previous deal,

84
00:04:51,880 --> 00:04:54,540
I was supposed to rebuild a healthy body for you.

85
00:04:54,560 --> 00:04:55,360
But I'm sorry.

86
00:04:55,840 --> 00:04:56,640
Right now,

87
00:04:57,240 --> 00:04:59,170
I might not be able to fully do that.

88
00:04:59,440 --> 00:05:00,570
So I must apologize.

89
00:05:00,960 --> 00:05:01,560
Yiyi,

90
00:05:01,920 --> 00:05:02,720
what's wrong?

91
00:05:02,960 --> 00:05:04,480
Did something happen to you?

92
00:05:04,480 --> 00:05:05,940
During that great battle,

93
00:05:06,360 --> 00:05:08,760
to prevent the power of their clash

94
00:05:08,760 --> 00:05:10,560
from hurting more innocent people,

95
00:05:10,560 --> 00:05:11,960
I used too much energy.

96
00:05:14,120 --> 00:05:14,760
So,

97
00:05:15,640 --> 00:05:17,440
I don't have enough energy left.

98
00:05:20,880 --> 00:05:22,040
But I will do my best

99
00:05:22,160 --> 00:05:23,360
to rebuild your body.

100
00:05:24,200 --> 00:05:25,920
It just might not reach the level of health

101
00:05:25,920 --> 00:05:27,380
we agreed upon in our deal.

102
00:05:29,440 --> 00:05:30,500
Please forgive me.

103
00:05:31,200 --> 00:05:32,730
After completing the deal,

104
00:05:32,760 --> 00:05:34,290
I will return to the source.

105
00:05:36,640 --> 00:05:37,960
Return to the source?

106
00:05:38,840 --> 00:05:40,440
Doesn't that mean you'll...

107
00:05:40,880 --> 00:05:41,840
Don't worry.

108
00:05:42,600 --> 00:05:43,530
After you leave,

109
00:05:43,640 --> 00:05:46,520
Lanqi Moyuan will gradually be swallowed by the seal.

110
00:05:46,520 --> 00:05:48,520
Even if I dissipate from this world,

111
00:05:48,560 --> 00:05:51,000
no one will have the power to destroy it anymore.

112
00:05:51,000 --> 00:05:51,760
This world

113
00:05:52,000 --> 00:05:53,330
will welcome a new life.

114
00:05:54,080 --> 00:05:56,010
That's not what I'm worried about.

115
00:05:56,240 --> 00:05:57,159
I mean you.

116
00:05:58,760 --> 00:06:00,760
You finally gained consciousness.

117
00:06:01,520 --> 00:06:03,120
Even though the one who wakes up next

118
00:06:03,120 --> 00:06:04,250
will no longer be me,

119
00:06:04,840 --> 00:06:05,480
it

120
00:06:05,920 --> 00:06:06,640
is still me.

121
00:06:08,720 --> 00:06:09,680
So,

122
00:06:10,280 --> 00:06:11,080
Yiyi,

123
00:06:12,280 --> 00:06:13,140
even you are...

124
00:06:14,640 --> 00:06:15,170
Lu Danyu,

125
00:06:15,920 --> 00:06:17,120
traveling with you

126
00:06:17,400 --> 00:06:18,400
has been my honor.

127
00:06:19,040 --> 00:06:20,040
After you go back,

128
00:06:20,480 --> 00:06:21,280
be happy.

129
00:06:59,400 --> 00:07:00,760
I'm back.

130
00:07:10,160 --> 00:07:11,080
Mom.

131
00:07:14,440 --> 00:07:14,840
Danyu.

132
00:07:15,080 --> 00:07:16,120
Danyu, you're awake.

133
00:07:16,120 --> 00:07:17,380
You're finally awake.

134
00:07:17,640 --> 00:07:18,170
My child.

135
00:07:18,320 --> 00:07:18,980
How are you?

136
00:07:19,360 --> 00:07:20,090
Does it hurt?

137
00:07:21,800 --> 00:07:22,240
Mom.

138
00:07:23,320 --> 00:07:24,400
I'm thirsty.

139
00:07:24,760 --> 00:07:25,090
Okay.

140
00:07:25,120 --> 00:07:25,480
Baby.

141
00:07:25,720 --> 00:07:27,180
I'll go get you some water.

142
00:07:29,280 --> 00:07:29,720
Dawei.

143
00:07:30,080 --> 00:07:31,140
The child is awake.

144
00:07:31,280 --> 00:07:32,560
She's finally awake.

145
00:07:32,640 --> 00:07:33,840
Come here quickly.
